{"lemma":"سَهْوُ","slug":"سَهْوُ","root":"س.ه.#","root_slug":"س-ه-_","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ه-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21108","n21109"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%87%D9%92%D9%88%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of سَهَا (sahā) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"oversight, inattention"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sahw/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21108","headword_ar":"سَهْوٌ","root":"shw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[an inf. n. used as an epithet,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Easy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a man, and to an affair, (K, TA,) and to an object of want: (TA:) and so [the fem.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sahowapN","text_ar":"سَهْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a mare; and applied to a she-mule as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy in pace, that does not fatigue her rider:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the epithet"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sahowN","text_ar":"سَهْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", however, is not applied to a he-mule: so in the T: (TA:) [but] it is applied to a he-camel, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy to ride:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sahowapN","text_ar":"سَهْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to a she-camel, (K, TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gentle, easy to ride:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAhK","text_ar":"رَاهٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAhK","text_ar":"سَاهٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a he-camel, means [likewise]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gentle"},{"kind":"text","text":"in pace; and so [the pls.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawaAhK rawaAhK","text_ar":"سَوَاهٍ رَوَاهٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to camels: (TA:) [and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sahowaA='u","text_ar":"سَهْوَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a mare; for] a certain mare was named"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~ahowaA='u","text_ar":"السَّهْوَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of the gentleness of her pace. (TA.) Also, applied to water,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cool, sweet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limpid; easy of descent in the throat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawosN sahowapN","text_ar":"قَوْسٌ سَهْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bow that is compliant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyHN sahowN","text_ar":"رِيحٌ سَهْوٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A gentle wind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a quiet, gentle wind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sihaA='N","text_ar":"سِهَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) a poet (said to be El-Hárith Ibn- 'Owf, TA) says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"tanaAwaHati Alr~ayaAHu lifaqodi EamorKw\n                      \n                     \n                        wakaAnato qabola maholikihi sihaA='aA"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The winds blew violently for the loss of 'Amr; but they were before his death"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quiet and gentle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN sahowapN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ سَهْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Soft land, without barrenness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~ahowu","text_ar":"السَّهْوُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The moon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the language of the Nabathæans. (JK.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n21109","headword_ar":"سِهْوٌ","root":"shw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sihowaA='N","text_ar":"سِهْوَا=ءٌ"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}